Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:26.79,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后的真相

Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:32.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇と遊ぶ星たちへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:36.85,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛を歌い　飽きつくした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:41.45,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏を灯し　雛菊の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:47.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に寄り添う爪の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:55.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唇から唇へと伝い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:59.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その温もりはどこへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:06.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿り付くあてはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:12.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたでなくちゃ　満たせない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私じゃなきゃ　許せなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:21.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　私はこの足で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:24.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:26.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぞっとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:31.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飼い殺しなら　救われる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも見事に　鍵は外れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:46.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私はまるで　鳥籠を欲している狂う籠鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:54.45,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘を抱いた花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:32.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗游戏的星斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:36.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱咏唱　我已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:41.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点亮夏季的雏菊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:47.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随梦境的爪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:55.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过双唇传递而来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:59.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份温存将何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:06.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有可以前往的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:12.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你　我得不到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我　是不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:21.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能用自己的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:24.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:26.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却感到心惊胆寒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:31.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果养我一生　我还可以得救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　锁却顺利打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:46.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宛如为渴求鸟笼而疯狂的笼中之鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:54.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱谎言的花

Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見てて　ご覧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　満ちぬけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:05.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溢れた傍から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:10.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えて　抜け殻に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:20.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流されて　辿り付く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:26.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現　蕩ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天この魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:43.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢　紡いだ夢を　どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:52.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その小指に絡めなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:56.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛んだ刺は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:03.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一つ抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:08.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取る　抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊　充满了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:05.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从溢出的一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:10.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐消失　变成了空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:20.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随波逐流　到达彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:26.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉于现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:43.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦　编织的梦境　请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:52.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请缠绕我的小指不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:56.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛的刺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:03.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根被拔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:08.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出　拔掉

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山河三岔路 别离之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护的是自己 是他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是常世的黑暗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非对错无法补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有终结的深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭转时空 打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难报之怨 我为您报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御景柚木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总有一天会成为地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是无法抵抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田老师从地狱少女的宿命解脱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:00:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会成为地狱少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友

Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公园里晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好路过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好再休息一会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就给你去泡热奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐你是一个人生活的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也很意外过的还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为每天都和父母通电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 海斗君的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是做什么工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学校的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是 普通的家庭主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 交换一下手机号码吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:03:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实刚才我说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的时候也会觉得一个人很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找个能说话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个伤 肯定是被人打了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小的孩子居然登陆地狱通信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 必须要阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 听说你今天回来很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啊 也不跟妈妈联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然撒谎说自己生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人头痛的哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我没有撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去玩的话就直说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小真可不能变成哥哥那样撒谎的孩子噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 妈妈马上就要临产了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不陪着怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天 住在城堡的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送来了舞会的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对于贫穷的灰姑娘来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有正装礼服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈因为是初产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情绪有些不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能原谅她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央生下来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会变回以前的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就又能去那个森林了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 4个人一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了 剩下的我来做就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在给你打电话没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时 魔法使出现了对她说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰姑娘 你是个心地善良的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做为奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我的魔法送你去参加舞会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}我成功了哟 那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一直没有给我回短信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就来见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 手机不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 一会来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前说想要玩的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我买了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 今天我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有事 也算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 妹妹就要出世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫真央
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈非常期待真央的出生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我也想帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就帮忙买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 那样的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都裂开了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我马上去换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥为什么总是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这样阴险的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要惩罚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫大津七海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我以前的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你多关照啊 海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是喜欢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Egg Man啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问了其他的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是那个很流行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海小姐好像找了很多地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 海斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有想马上就成为你的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先成为你无话不说的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的后母虐子的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是够任性的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己怀上了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对没有血缘的孩子另眼相看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:10:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 为什么不对父亲说这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说来 确实很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话海斗君就会登陆地狱通信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去商量下如何啊 和你父母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们关系不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊里是下任的地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在家 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她们出去吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 已经用了三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该寿终正寝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个帽子是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候给你买顶新的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 随便扔掉确实有点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 那顶帽子对妈妈来说也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被邻居的夫人嘲笑很破旧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你们家的孩子总是戴着同一顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 你总是这样惯他可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央也快出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让海斗振作一点可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 对不起 妈妈说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱 少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山童
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要和我说 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你登陆了地狱通信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要流放的人是 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听得到 海斗君内心的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想救海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我实话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊 海斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 我会给你买新的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的Egg Man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个湖泊很深噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去的话就上不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 你听到我说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽让我们担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗要是发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们幸福的家庭就不存在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要 回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能依靠地狱通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子虐待孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听你说有很重要的事才过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君身上有不少的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你可能不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个年龄段的男孩子经常会有擦伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被殴打 被掐的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我来问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗他亲口说是妈妈造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我知道的 海斗君内心的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是正经家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再说这种不着边际的话 我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人早就发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过装作没看见罢了 为求自保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 海斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快接电话 妈妈 快接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我还想跟你商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快接啊 快接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母子手册带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了 那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走好 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗 不坐车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个 海斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去森林吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前不是很想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔父子俩也要单独相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了一个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却想不到一个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 海斗君会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出来 地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出来 你在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见海斗君 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到之后你又打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是无法阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好跟他说的话 一定能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的地狱 其实在人的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去亲眼见证下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君 海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我会扔旋转的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸已经筋疲力尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 你喜欢妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人又漂亮 做的料理也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既清纯又开朗 是男学生眼中的梦中情人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的妈妈选择了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸我 真的不想再这样看着妈妈垮下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗君 快逃 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 爸爸想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让妈妈抚养两个孩子也许真的有点勉强她了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我实在是没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜呢 真央
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有我和爸爸在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的手 好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊 海斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗 我会给你买新的 快到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Egg man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个湖泊很深噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去的话就再也上不来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惊人的家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看到地狱之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能这样好像什么事也没发生过似的笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们总有一天会意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己曾经犯下的罪行的恶果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}山童
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}是 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会来到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场雪将会将所有罪行深深掩盖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海斗也想试着钓鱼么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以噢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 我为你消除

Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园济佳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.44,0:24:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恨她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是恨她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子很漂亮 而且很亮丽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.34,0:24:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我做影子也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.43,0:24:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为这样就让我感到满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.19,0:24:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.08,0:24:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与生俱来的因果缘分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 花与月
